{"tid":1405176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突發！）一位高盛執行董事表示公司一班高層都會響應8月5日罷工！","createTime":"2019-08-04T08:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T10:08:32.000Z","uid":293289,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"520656fd6d5855066d7073f871791156d44a083c","tid":1405176,"uid":293289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rs0f68q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frs0f68q.png&h=18aab0a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢係我識左幾年的行家，平時大家都會放工得閒去下飲野，過去佢一直都係好似我之前咁，政治冷感，工作賺錢永遠係第一位。但今次，佢竟然主動同我講：「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府今次真係太過份，我地今次點都要企出來做d野！</span></span>」「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我身邊好多和理非的Goldman同事今次都表明星期一會罷工，要同香港人齊上齊落！</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n呢位ibanker朋友cap左圖比我，係佢如何透過wtsapp直接同佢公司老闆講8月5日要罷工，內容大意是：「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老闆，我諗得好清楚，星期一我唔返工了，我想去金鐘添馬公園集會，因為我要同香港人一齊共同進退，表達訴求！</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n除左呢位好友，連同過去幾日我地收集到的職員證，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">高盛及其他投資銀行有幾百位高層員工響應今次罷工</span></span>！並表明支持香港人爭取民主的訴求！<br />\n<br />\n而暫時<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一共有超過兩千個金融界人士已經表明會8月5日罷工！裡面基本上咩職位、咩公司都有</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n香港人，你決定好罷工未？我地一齊齊上齊落吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n送兩張關於罷工的錦囊給大家：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xoz8HHD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXoz8HHD.png&h=0cd68f96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RtUgRA8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRtUgRA8.png&h=6b1c02ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相片來自: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/FinanceFellow/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FFinanceFellow%2F&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUBw4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=76a83f55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank